    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "> Is this prompted by a problem in the new interface? The idea of landing it is to discover and fix any problems, so I don't want to make it too easy to switch back.\n\nNo, just rebasing my current work on Pygments. I can likely do it without that, But I'll have to understand how prompt toolkit work. Also the Prompt toolkit interface does not seem to support LightBG and Linux Color (which map terminal theming by using short ansi sequence) which is super painful as current theme hurt my eyes. And without this feature I would likely not want to use the prompt toolkit interface. \n"
  },
